      • AbstractRequirementGroupAssertion

        public AbstractRequirementGroupAssertion(ResultStatus status,
                                         String quantifier,
                                         Operator operator)
        Represents an assertion over the results of performing a set of assessments that applies to a group of requirements.
        Parameters:
        status - the required assessment result status for each requirement in the group
        quantifier - the number of requirements that must pass or null if all must pass
        operator - the type of comparison operator to use
